==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Immobilize
<hw>Im*mob"i*lize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>im-</ets> in + <ets>mobilize</ets>; cf. f.
<ets>immobiliser</ets>.]</ety> <def>To make immovable; in surgery, to
make immovable (a naturally mobile part, as a joint) by the use of
splints, or stiffened bandages.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Immoble</ent>⟦br⟧
